{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/node.js/2020-10-13-node-version/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>n 모듈</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">n</code>\t<code class=\"language-text\">Node.js</code> 버전을 관리해주는 플러그인</li>\n<li>다양한 버전을 선택하여 설치 가능 (최신 버전, 안정 버전, LTS, 특정 버전)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><strong>install n</strong></h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># n모듈 설치</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># node 안정버전 설치</span>\n$ n stable\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 노드버전 확인</span>\n$ node -v\nv11.10.0 \n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># lts버전 설치</span>\n$ n lts\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 특정버전 설치 ex> $ n &lt;version> </span>\n$ n <span class=\"token number\">10.0</span>.0\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 버전삭제 </span>\n$ n <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> <span class=\"token number\">10.0</span>.0</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h1><strong>npm upgrade</strong></h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">//npm 버전 확인\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> -v\n<span class=\"token number\">3.1</span>.0\n\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g <span class=\"token function\">npm</span>\n/usr/local/bin/npm -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npm-cli.js\n/usr/local/bin/npx -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npx-cli.js\n+ npm@6.8.0\nadded <span class=\"token number\">2</span> packages from <span class=\"token number\">2</span> contributors, removed <span class=\"token number\">2</span> packages and updated <span class=\"token number\">7</span> packages <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span>.345s\n\n<span class=\"token variable\">$npm</span> -v\n<span class=\"token number\">3.10</span>.0</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2010-10-13","title":"[Node.js] node 버전 관리: n 모듈","tags":["Node.js","dev env"]},"fields":{"slug":"/node.js/2020-10-13-node-version/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/node.js/2020-10-13-node-version/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2827402515"]}